thread.title: Natural Gas Holds Steady on Warmer Forecasts
thread.title_full: Natural Gas Holds Steady on Warmer Forecasts - WSJ

author: Timothy Puko
title: Natural Gas Holds Steady on Warmer Forecasts
text:
Natural gas prices are holding close to unchanged Wednesday as weather forecasts continue to warm, pushing stronger expectations for demand and helping to prop up the market.
Prices for the front-month September contract was down 0.2 cent, or 0.1%, at $2.683 a million British thermal units on the New York Mercantile Exchange. September options...
